ealthy male subjects. <i>Clinical drug investigation</i> 31(10) 727–733. DOI:<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.2165/11589010-000000000-00000\">10.2165/11589010-000000000-00000</a>  PUBMED:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21877765/\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21877765</a></p></li></ol></body></html>",
